@node "Introd" " MV Status - Introduction"
@next "disclaim"
@prev "main"

 Yes, you are right, there are already many Status doors for DayDream, but...

 Simply, I do not like that all those STAT doors I'd seen are not
 display-mode sensitive, and all of them have fixed outlook.

 So I decided to write my very first DayDream Door in C.

 MV Stat is fully look-configurable, there are only few thing you must
 respect, so, read about in @{" configuration " Link Config} about it.


@endnode

