@node Registration " MV Status - Registration"
@next "Author"
@prev "user"

        @{fg shine}@{u} REGISTRATION @{uu}@{fg text}

 MV Status Door is EMailware, that means if you like (or not) door,
 you are supposed to send EMAIL to @{"author" Link author}.

 If you find any bug or have some idea for improving MV Status Door, 
 feel free to contact @{"author" Link author}.

 Door is no crippled in any way.

 Look at @{"other Mad Virgin products" Link MVProd}.



@endnode

