@node MV-SOT2.LZX " MV Produtcts - Start On Time "
@prev MVProd

This is a very useful and fully tested Scheduler utility which allow sysops
to program events. 

It's fast & easy to use & tested!

@endnode 

@node MV-SRT10.LZX " MV Products - Set Remaining Time"

It's a small utility for DayDream BBS which allow you to easy solve daily
time problem for GUEST account on your DD BBS.


@endnode

@node MVM129F5.LHA " MV Products - MV MAIL 1.29f5 "

MV Mail door is fully featured Blue Wave DOOR for your DayDream BBS !
ALL MAIL functions are fully operational and hardly tested!

MV Mail fix many problems you had with Grab 2.0, and much more... 

Download DEMO version NOW! and see what are you missing.


@endnode

